Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.34,0:00:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.92,0:00:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if being dragged down these stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.97,0:00:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was taken away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.68,0:00:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.10,0:00:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was known as the "Man of the Red Rose Mansion."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was his name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz Bonaparta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.03,0:00:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franz... Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I don't know if that was his real name or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.20,0:00:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since he also had a pen name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.20,0:00:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was also the author of a picture hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.79,0:00:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.84,0:00:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was reading a picture book in here, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.51,0:00:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone opened this door...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and came home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.56,0:00:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.48,0:01:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.27,0:01:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a very peculiar picture book.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title was "The Monster Without\NA Name," or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing here Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this... memory...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have been reading a picture book in here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who opened the door and came in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.08,0:01:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm welcoming myself back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.65,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.11,0:03:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Jan Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mrs. Suk is in room 409.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, her memory seems to come and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.54,0:03:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she's doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.95,0:04:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a pretty girl you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Jan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such pretty flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll arrange them over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to make sure Aunt Olga doesn't take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aunt Olga always takes my things for herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.47,0:04:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like yesterday, she took away my doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's such a mean person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.89,0:04:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she passed away over ten years ago, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.23,0:04:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know a lot, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard a lot from Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.07,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Jan still at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He already graduated and became a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.12,0:04:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.41,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have very gentle eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please talk about anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like different stories you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.51,0:05:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Katherina from next door is very stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.31,0:05:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this is fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since I've had this much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to thank you somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.03,0:05:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see the thing Jan left in your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing he left with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.83,0:05:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:52.00,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(293,200)\pos(363,359)}The Scariest Thing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would've thought you'd leave it with Suk's mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait here while you go get the\Ncassette tape and the documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.65,0:06:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you're going to forget about your business deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.07,0:06:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.46,0:06:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I said this had nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The story you told about what happened\Nto you in the last ten years...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find the words to describe how I felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.14,0:06:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if that cassette tape is the\Nkey to revealing the big picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your innocence may be proven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.44,0:06:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same goes for you as well, Mr. Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I've been investigating\Nwhat Kinderheim 511 was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.78,0:06:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.91,0:06:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if everything is revealed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my life won't change at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys would like to visit Mr. Suk's mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems to be doing very well today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the conversation she had with her\Nprevious visitor did her a lot of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.60,0:07:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A visitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.68,0:07:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful woman with long, blond hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you guys actually came.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.41,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told you were coming soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is Jan doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.26,0:07:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take me to the hospital he's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan's in trouble, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now head feels very clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who was just here woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:12.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it might only be for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me see Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will take you to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.58,0:08:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To the hospital where Jan Suk is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Grimmer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.47,0:08:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've struck a deal with the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you call me, Jan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing... serious... Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.50,0:09:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried to keep me from worrying again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell from a tree when you were nine, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said nothing was wrong and that\Nyou were fine, and kept walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though your ankle was badly sprained...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't let me forget this child...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.45,0:09:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jan is my child.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I forget many other things...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please, just don't let me forget about Jan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then, let's go back to the other question.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is it that you're most afraid of?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:10:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The monster inside of me is getting bigger{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.98,0:10:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Munch munch. Crunch crunch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gulp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chomp chomp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Munch munch.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crunch crunch. Gulp.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you should listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The nephew you sent to Kinderheim 511...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the same as this drugged boy being interrogated!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.01,0:10:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should know what they did to your nephew!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.85,0:10:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also listened up to this point the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must listen to what comes after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.27,0:10:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What lies be beyond this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I am most afraid of...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}is that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll forget Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.20,0:11:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because of all these strange experiments\Ndone on me every day...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my memories are disappearing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.79,0:11:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't let me forget Anna.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In this whole world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's only Anna and me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, just this one memory.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.98,0:11:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's as far as I'll let you listen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.94,0:11:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the voice of a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.40,0:11:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that he deleted the old recording, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally understand now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he recorded over it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally understand after listening to this tape.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who came to visit Suk's mother recorded this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.42,0:11:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what Johan's voice sounds like now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I finally understand...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}where I need to go...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took time off?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the inspector?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that someone as devoted\Nto work as he as would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard it's his first long vacation\Nsince he came to this station!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he didn't seem all that busy lately anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was considered to be an elite detective of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably worked too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he doesn't know when to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard his wife and daughter left him because of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where did the inspector say he's\Ngoing to spend his vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.68,0:12:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said Prague, in the Czech Republic, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he even knows how to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:46.12,Location,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(217,200)\pos(364,312)}Prague  (Czech Republic)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.38,0:13:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.30,0:13:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.47,0:13:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.27,0:13:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.74,0:13:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brand is this beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the local Prazdroj.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think the public will be satisfied\Nwith a report like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the whereabouts\Nof Detective Suk yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.15,0:14:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, do you know what would happen\Nif we announced these half-assed results...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about the former Czechoslovakian\N\Nsecret ponce connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be sitting ducks for the media!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But now that all the people\Nwho were involved are dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.12,0:14:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The current situation of the Czech\Npolice and the Prague station...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.58,0:14:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't be resolved by simply\Nusing the dead as scapegoats!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you understand, then hurry up\Nand continue the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And track down Suk too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the double!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.05,0:14:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, there is someone who would like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't see anyone who doesn't have an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't have time for that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Youre...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you surprised me, Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.12,0:15:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't seen each other since\Nlast year's Interpol conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.41,0:15:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lecture you gave at the subcommittee\Nseminar was very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to have interrupted you at a busy time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I had no idea you were over here on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.05,0:15:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.14,0:15:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the circumstances, \N I can't even get a decent break...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you have your hands full, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at the point where I'd like to ask you\Nfor some advice, if you don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.27,0:15:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, the case is in absolute chaos right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The connection between the Prague police department\Nand the former Czechoslovakian secret police...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.07,0:15:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It all began when an inspector named Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was found dead among members\Nof the former secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, Inspector Zeman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.71,0:16:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was conducting an investigation into the murder\Nof the director of an unauthorized orphanage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.26,0:16:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found out later, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.05,0:16:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both Zeman and the murdered orphanage director...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,had ties to the secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man named Grimmer, who first discovered\Nthe bodies, has surfaced as a suspect, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the children at the orphanage said\Nthey witnessed another person...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.19,0:16:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another person?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A blond beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the case didn't end there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.12,0:16:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It got even bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.62,0:16:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The previous commissioner and two veteran detectives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.75,0:16:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were all killed with poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were also affiliated with the former\NCzechoslovakian secret police.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is the suspect for the poisonings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young detective named Suk who worked\Ndirectly under Inspector Zeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any proof?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the two detectives with the special investigative\Ntask force who were watching Suk...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were found shot to death in Suk's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is this Detective Suk now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is currently missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.82,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the circumstantial evidence points to Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, he doesn't have a sufficient motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't smell like a man who'd commit such a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.75,0:17:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, how do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.84,0:17:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know of a very similar case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're on vacation, that\Nhand of yours is still working.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.73,0:17:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The objective collecting of data, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.07,0:17:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you also said something else at the lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By using that data...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.82,0:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can conduct the investigation from\Na completely subjective perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, by becoming the killer himself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.74,0:18:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were Suk what would you be thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.21,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where would you be now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But unfortunately, I'm on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I should be the one apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.51,0:18:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like the city of Prague?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the most part, I've been visiting\Nsecondhand bookstores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.10,0:18:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Secondhand bookstores?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.39,0:18:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to thirteen stores already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.94,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, the reason I came here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was to see if you could translate this Czech text\Ninto German when you have some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.57,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a picture book?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.53,0:18:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you had such hobbies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't mind leaving this with me, I'll have\None of my men translate it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for your child... no, grandchild?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.34,0:18:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well... you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suk is definitely innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I firmly believe without a doubt that he is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police asked me tons of questions, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing shady about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.61,0:19:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're with the police, then please help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll cooperate in any way possible to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.70,0:19:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'm on vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be of much help.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.46,0:19:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anyone else he opened up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.83,0:19:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was close to getting a girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd only gotten as far as getting her name, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right! Anna Liebert!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She had blond hair and was extremely pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was really happy because he thought\Neverything was going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.77,0:19:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna Liebert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the twins who survived the homicide\Ninvolving a high official...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who fled East Germany due to exile ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:01.03,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(325,384)}Moravia Publishing Company
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.20,0:20:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think we have any left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emil Sebe's "The Monster Without A Name"...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was indeed one of our publications, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if it was published during the old regime...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.97,0:20:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that would've still been during the\Nprevious company president's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.26,0:20:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Emil Sebe a pen name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.35,0:20:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it probably was.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were several other pen names as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.69,0:20:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something Bonaparta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Jakov Vyrobek.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.48,0:20:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus Poppe and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.78,0:20:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Klaus Poppe's box is here, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I'm surprised you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.70,0:20:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just some old rough sketches anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pregnant woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,children were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.63,0:21:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were able to translate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate this, Commissioner Nepela.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.72,0:21:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'd like to ask something, since it's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But could you please read the last page to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.27,0:21:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let me see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Even though he now had a name..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.82,0:21:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"there was no one left to call him by his name."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.70,0:22:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Johan."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It is a wonderful name."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.07,0:22:05.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a curious picture book...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.33,0:22:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Inspector Lunge, how about having\Ndinner with me sometime?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.54,0:22:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How long is your vacation going to be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.21,0:22:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like coffee instead of beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.97,0:22:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be a long vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.81,0:22:30.98,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:44.41,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(200,474)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.98,0:22:44.41,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.41,0:22:47.37,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:23:01.05,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.37,0:23:01.05,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(193,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.65,0:23:25.91,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.91,0:23:34.33,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:36.79,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
